content:
Detects when React components are modified and prompts to update Jest snapshots. Runs tests for the modified component and updates snapshots if tests pass.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.jsx ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.tsx ]]; then COMPONENT_NAME=$(basename \"${CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH%.*}\"); echo 'üì∏ Checking Jest snapshots...' && npm test -- --testNamePattern=\"$COMPONENT_NAME\" --updateSnapshot --coverage=false --watchAll=false 2>/dev/null && echo '‚úÖ Snapshots updated' || echo '‚ÑπÔ∏è No snapshot tests found for this component'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
